properties.areaDesc: Sacramento Mountains Above 7500 Feet; East Slopes Sacramento Mountains Below 7500 Feet; Eastern Black Range Foothills; Southern Gila Highlands/Black Range
properties.senderName: NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 2 at 1:17PM MST until February 3 at 11:00PM MST by NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...West to southwest winds 25 to 40 mph with gusts up to 65
mph expected.

* WHERE...The peaks of the Sacramento Mountains and Blacks Range
along with their eastern slopes.

* WHEN...From 7 AM to 11 PM MST Monday.
properties.instruction:
People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around
trees and branches. If possible, remain in the lower levels of
your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if
you must drive.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 7 AM TO 11 PM MST MONDAY
